column2:
For example, if using terminal:
curl --request POST \
  --url https://api.climatiq.io/energy/v1/fuel \
  --header "Authorization: Bearer $CLIMATIQ_API_KEY" \
  --data '{
    "fuel_type": "biodiesel_bio_100",
    "amount": {
        "volume": 5000,
        "volume_unit": "l"
    },
    "region": "GB",
    "year": 2023
}'
